code: @Override public void readFrom(StreamInput in) throws IOException {     super.readFrom(in).     int size = in.readVInt().     mappings = new ExpressionRoleMapping[size].     for (int i = 0. i < size. i++) {         mappings[i] = new ExpressionRoleMapping(in).     } }

@Override public void writeTo(StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     super.writeTo(out).     out.writeVInt(mappings.length).     for (ExpressionRoleMapping mapping : mappings) {         mapping.writeTo(out).     } }
